                     <interp inst="t18440819-1995-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 purse, value 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 sovereign, 1 sovereign, 1 shilling, 2 sixpences, and 1 half-franc; the property of <persName id="t18440819-name-561" type="victimName">
